      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# FrameWeaver Post-Processing Demo\n\nThis workflow demonstrates the post-processing chain without any LTX generation. It works with any image batch.\n\n**Pipeline:** Load images \u2192 FW_ColorMatch (match to reference) \u2192 FW_CinematicPolish (sharpen) \u2192 FW_FilmGrain (add texture) \u2192 FW_LUTApply (color grade) \u2192 Save\n\n**Tips:** Adjust FW_CinematicPolish mode (unsharp/laplacian/sobel) and strength. Start FW_FilmGrain at 0.25 intensity. Use FW_LUTCreate to generate custom .cube LUTs from hex palettes."
      ]
    },
